subject: Horse Racing
Horses
Breeding of Animals
lead_paragraph: Lisa’s Booby Trap, who won the Loudonville Stakes on Friday, was purchased for $2,000 by Tim Snyder this past winter. He was recently offered $500,000 for Lisa’s Booby Trap. No sale.
